    <data key="d0">DISH Network: Multi-Account Provisioning and Networking with Service Catalog and Control Tower</data>
    <data key="d1">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=62E9ggjGS8I</data>
    <data key="d2">DISH Network utilizes an ITSM-driven self-service workflow to scale account creation. Control Tower handles the baseline account vending, Service Catalog deploys standard networking, and the Serverless Transit Network Orchestrator (STNO) automatically configures transit gateway attachments based on resource tags.</data>
    <data key="d3">control, interactive</data>
    <data key="d4">True</data>
